  m_Name: Level02_Intro
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelIntroData
  levelTitle: Beneath the Surface
  levelContext: "Something is spreading beneath the surface.\n\n\nEurasian watermilfoil
    is forming dense mats in lakes, blocking sunlight, lowering oxygen, and choking
    out native plants. Fish habitats are already being affected.\n\n\nIt spreads
    easily through tiny fragments carried by boats and currents.\n\nTrash infiltrates
    our lakes. Help clean our water and protect the spieces that reside in it. \n<color=#FF0000><size=30><b>Mission:</b></size>\n<size=23>Remove
    infestations and stop the spread between lakes.</size></color>"
